  "Richard Li is a son of one of Hong Kong's wealthiest billionaires Li Ka-Shing. He chairs Asia-based investment company Pacific Century group.  ",
  "Pacific Century owns most of life insurance company FWD, which operates in seven countries across Asia, including Hong Kong and Singapore.",
  "The group also has interests in businesses spanning financial services, technology and property. ",
  "Li established a communications and media empire with  PCCW, a Hong Kong-based company which controls the city's largest mobile phone operator HKT.",
  "In July 2019, FWD acquired the life insurance business of Siam Commercial Bank for $3 billion."
